Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:16.74,Title,,0,0,0,,The Boy Like the Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.98,end,,0,0,0,,End
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolnie bought so many perfumes;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I must not break them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,come play with my toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear son,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy is busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch it, Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re such a slowpoke! You’re no help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the day…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my backpack in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re amazing; thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone over there needs my help;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not as good as my past self.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s these waste fishing nets again;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they’ve gotten me so many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,These waste fishing nets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,not only destroy the marine ecosystem,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,they also endanger our safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m in a hurry; I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Crab, you dropped something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of breeze is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m suddenly feeling a strong power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,infuse into me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like my whole body is full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Weslie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a fragment on that taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t keep up;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s odd;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,why am I running so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you ran so fast just now;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,how did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t let them know that I used that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s actually the result of hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re amazing, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look like I’ll have to exercise, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a very important contract
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that I need to get to a suburban company right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll make sure to have it sent on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My new coral tiara!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So many orders;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when am I going to finish delivering them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting star fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it’s too late to make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My skateboard is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anyone help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re standing on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I feel fatigued all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s because you used too much of the Super Fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing you didn’t keep using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What’ll happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Death
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,won’t happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Paralysis
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,won’t happen, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you just tell me all at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you’ll get a runny nose,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,chills,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,hot flashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a sore throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and generalized muscle pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In short,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,severe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you must not use it ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting severe colds is very dangerous at your age!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy stole our fragment container!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the fragment container!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re cheating, Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of hero are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not trying to be any sort of hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fellow kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m headed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy stole our fragment container and ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll chase him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All the fragments are mine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowy, with how slow you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think you can catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This world now belongs to the young wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, give me back the fragment container!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, you have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can’t catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he’s lost control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find a way to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hold him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But he’s moving too fast;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we have no way to hold him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have an idea…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t use that fan again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the matter, Uncle Crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy will face very severe consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if he uses the Super Fan again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of your body, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But there’s nothing else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re right;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to rely on my own strength to solve this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, Paddi, Uncle Crab,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys go to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie, Sparky, Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys go to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My fragments!
